---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Business Ideas — Lucas Sommer" description="A running list of business ideas Lucas Sommer has evaluated, is exploring, or is putting out there for someone else to build.">

  <article class="ideas-page container">

    <div class="ideas-hero">
      <h1>Business Ideas</h1>
      <p class="ideas-intro">
        Ideas I've evaluated, am exploring, or am putting out there for someone else to build. Every idea here has been pressure-tested using my <a href="/resources/ideation-flow">ideation framework</a> — sized by market, priced by margin, and ranked by feasibility.
      </p>
      <p class="ideas-sub">
        Ideas are cheap. Execution is everything. If you want to build one of these, <a href="https://twitter.com/lucasbsommer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">reach out</a>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Filters -->
    <div class="idea-filters">
      <button class="filter-btn active" data-filter="all">All</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="open"><span class="filter-dot" style="background:var(--status-active-text);"></span> Open</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="exploring"><span class="filter-dot" style="background:var(--status-exploring-text);"></span> Exploring</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="building"><span class="filter-dot" style="background:var(--status-building-text);"></span> Building</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="parked"><span class="filter-dot" style="background:var(--text-tertiary);"></span> Parked</button>
    </div>

    <!-- Ideas Grid -->
    <div class="ideas-grid">

      <!-- IDEA TEMPLATE - Replace these with real ideas -->

      <article class="idea-card" data-status="open">
        <div class="idea-top">
          <div class="idea-number">01</div>
          <span class="idea-status idea-status-open">Open</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="idea-title">[Idea Name]</h2>
        <p class="idea-tagline">One-line description of what it is and who it's for.</p>
        <div class="idea-tags">
          <span class="tag">Category</span>
          <span class="tag">Market Size</span>
        </div>
        <div class="idea-details">
          <div class="idea-detail">
            <div class="idea-detail-label">The Problem</div>
            <p>What's broken, slow, expensive, or painful in the market today.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="idea-detail">
            <div class="idea-detail-label">The Opportunity</div>
            <p>Why now? Why this gap exists. Rough TAM if known.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="idea-detail">
            <div class="idea-detail-label">Who Should Build It</div>
            <p>The type of founder or team this idea is a fit for.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="idea-card" data-status="exploring">
        <div class="idea-top">
          <div class="idea-number">02</div>
          <span class="idea-status idea-status-exploring">Exploring</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="idea-title">[Idea Name]</h2>
        <p class="idea-tagline">One-line description of what it is and who it's for.</p>
        <div class="idea-tags">
          <span class="tag">Category</span>
          <span class="tag">Market Size</span>
        </div>
        <div class="idea-details">
          <div class="idea-detail">
            <div class="idea-detail-label">The Problem</div>
            <p>What's broken, slow, expensive, or painful in the market today.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="idea-detail">
            <div class="idea-detail-label">The Opportunity</div>
            <p>Why now? Why this gap exists. Rough TAM if known.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="idea-detail">
            <div class="idea-detail-label">Current Status</div>
            <p>What I'm doing about it right now.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="idea-card" data-status="parked">
        <div class="idea-top">
          <div class="idea-number">03</div>
          <span class="idea-status idea-status-parked">Parked</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="idea-title">[Idea Name]</h2>
        <p class="idea-tagline">One-line description of what it is and who it's for.</p>
        <div class="idea-tags">
          <span class="tag">Category</span>
        </div>
        <div class="idea-details">
          <div class="idea-detail">
            <div class="idea-detail-label">The Problem</div>
            <p>What's broken, slow, expensive, or painful.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="idea-detail">
            <div class="idea-detail-label">Why I Parked It</div>
            <p>What made me decide not to pursue this now — wrong market, wrong timing, wrong fit, etc.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="ideas-cta">
      <h3>Have an idea to add?</h3>
      <p>I collect ideas from conversations, problems I run into, and gaps I notice. If you want to riff on one of these — or share your own — hit me up on <a href="https://twitter.com/lucasbsommer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Twitter</a>.</p>
    </div>

  </article>

  <script is:inline>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      var buttons = document.querySelectorAll('.filter-btn');
      var cards = document.querySelectorAll('.idea-card');

      buttons.forEach(function(btn) {
        btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
          buttons.forEach(function(b) { b.classList.remove('active'); });
          btn.classList.add('active');
          var filter = btn.dataset.filter;

          cards.forEach(function(card) {
            if (filter === 'all' || card.dataset.status === filter) {
              card.style.display = '';
            } else {
              card.style.display = 'none';
            }
          });
        });
      });
    });
  </script>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .ideas-page {
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  /* Hero */
  .ideas-hero {
    padding-top: 4rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .ideas-hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -1.5px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .ideas-intro {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .ideas-sub {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  /* Filters */
  .idea-filters {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 0 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .filter-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.4rem 0.85rem;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    background: var(--surface-1);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
  }

  .filter-btn:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .filter-btn.active {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #ffffff;
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .filter-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  /* Ideas Grid */
  .ideas-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .idea-card {
    background: var(--surface-1);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.75rem;
    transition: border-color 0.15s ease, background-color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .idea-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
  }

  .idea-top {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .idea-number {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .idea-status {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
  }

  .idea-status-open {
    background: var(--status-active-bg);
    color: var(--status-active-text);
  }

  .idea-status-exploring {
    background: var(--status-exploring-bg);
    color: var(--status-exploring-text);
  }

  .idea-status-building {
    background: var(--status-building-bg);
    color: var(--status-building-text);
  }

  .idea-status-parked {
    background: var(--surface-2);
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }

  .idea-title {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .idea-tagline {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
  }

  .idea-tags {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .idea-tags .tag {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    background: var(--surface-2);
    padding: 0.15rem 0.55rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xs);
  }

  .idea-details {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .idea-detail-label {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .idea-detail p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .idea-detail p strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  /* CTA */
  .ideas-cta {
    background: var(--surface-1);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.75rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    transition: border-color 0.15s ease, background-color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .ideas-cta h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .ideas-cta p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* Mobile */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .ideas-hero { padding-top: 3rem; }
    .ideas-hero h1 { font-size: 1.75rem; }
    .ideas-intro { font-size: 1rem; }
    .idea-card { padding: 1.35rem; }
    .idea-title { font-size: 1.15rem; }
  }
</style>
